reviewText: This video is pretty much what I expected.  Since the items were on film originally, the reproduction is better than I thought it would be.  I did think that there might be trailers for up-coming movies, but was disappointed in that.

This was not a good purchase.  I got the same quality on-line looking at You Tube.  As another reviewer points out, the picture is tiny only about 1/4 of the screen and is not really suitable for showing at a movie night.

These were originally downloaded from Internet Moving Archives.  The videos only fit the center of the screen.

Low quality, I don't recommend.
